# Awesome Zeronet [![Awesome](https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg)](https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome)

> Cool links for the Zeronet
> links with "+" in front of the name could be host nsfw content or other stuff... Be careful...

## Video hosting sites

*   +["Youtube"](http://127.0.0.1:43110/149EPBN4hQRpwj5TcoPETepnoXHCUXzaCN/) - a decentralized video sharing platform
*   []

## Services

Contributions welcome! Read the [contribution guidelines](contributing.md) first.

*   [ZeroUpdate](http://127.0.0.1:43110/1UPDatEDxnvHDo7TXvq6AEBARfNkyfxsp/) - an decentralized Update Service for the Zeronet client

*   [ZeroMail](http://127.0.0.1:43110/Mail.ZeroNetwork.bit/) - an decentralized Mail System

*   [ZeroName](http://127.0.0.1:43110/1Name2NXVi1RDPDgf5617UoW7xA6YrhM9F/) - an decentralized ZeroNet domain name registry (.bit domains)

*   [Git Center](http://127.0.0.1:43110/1GitLiXB6t5r8vuU2zC6a8GYj9ME6HMQ4t/) - an decentralized Git Repository System

*   [ZeroShortener](http://127.0.0.1:43110/0sh.bit/) - an ZeroNet Link Shortener

## ID providers

*   [ZeroID](http://127.0.0.1:43110/zeroid.bit/) - an (not so) decentralized ID provider

*   [id@Zeroverse](http://127.0.0.1:43110/zeroverse.bit/) - an other ID provider

## Tools

Cool Tools to help you.

*   [ZeroDB](http://127.0.0.1:43110/ZeroDB.bit/) - visual editor to create dbschema files
